com.mesosphere.sdk.specification

Class DefaultService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mesosphere.sdk.specification.DefaultService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Service

    public class DefaultService
extends java.lang.Object
implements Service
    This class is a default implementation of the Service interface. It serves mainly as an example with hard-coded values for "user", and "master-uri", and failover timeouts. More sophisticated services may want to implement the Service interface directly.

    Customizing the runtime user for individual tasks may be accomplished by customizing the 'user' field on CommandInfo returned by TaskSpec.getCommand().
